Package: tinyshinyserver
Type: Package
Title: Tiny Shiny Server - Lightweight Multi-App Shiny Proxy
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Author", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "author@example.com")
    )
Description: A lightweight, WebSocket-enabled proxy server for hosting multiple
    Shiny applications with automatic health monitoring, session management,
    and resource cleanup. Provides a simple entry point 'start_tss()' to run the
    server using a JSON configuration file.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
